OL,3,CTory candidates face election betting
OL,4,Cinvestigation: What are the rules?
OL,6,FEssentially, it concerns knowledge
OL,7,Fthat individuals outside any given
OL,8,Findustry or trade are not aware of,
OL,9,Fand which could be inappropriately
OL,10,Fused for financial gain (e.g. the
OL,11,Fplacement of bets).
OL,13,FThe Gambling Commission regards inside
OL,14,Finformation as knowledge "known by an
OL,15,Findividual or individuals as a result
OL,16,Fof their role in connection with an
OL,17,Fevent and which is not in the public
OL,18,Fdomain".
