OL,3,CTory candidates face election betting
OL,4,Cinvestigation: What are the rules?
OL,6,FThe law makes plain that a person
OL,7,Ffound guilty of using inside
OL,8,Finformation to bet could be considered
OL,9,Fto be cheating, which is covered under
OL,10,Fthe Gambling Act 2005.
OL,12,FSection 42 of the legislation states
OL,13,Fthat it is an offence for anyone to
OL,14,Fcheat at gambling or do anything that
OL,15,Fmight assist another person to cheat.
